{"tid":497721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【趣遊樓市】元朗未來的大型發展（脫苦海）","createTime":"2017-12-13T05:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T05:30:04.000Z","uid":10958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f0bcd8648a62c3d70d711a08e8ad37c6851e7329","tid":497721,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>【趣遊樓市】元朗未來的大型發展（脫苦海）</strong><br />\n<br />\n上星期講到屯門的大型發展，今次講元朗區，現時有三個新開發區正在進行規劃及建設，其一是地跨屯門元朗，位於天水圍以西，青山公路以北的洪水橋新展發區，其二是青山公路及元朗市以南的元朗南新發展區，其三則是錦田南新發展區。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n相信大家都聽過多次有關洪水橋的發展，作為先頭部隊的洪福邨已經入伙，另外一個進度較快的是天水圍站對面的居屋屏欣苑，預計在明年入伙。根據建議發展大綱圖，當中不少均以公營房屋發展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/N2xMk0FCJrHv03s83WxAbw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/22d50dfb16d1b331b7b4d132b808360f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FN2xMk0FCJrHv03s83WxAbw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F22d50dfb16d1b331b7b4d132b808360f&h=5dd57287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外一個新發展區是元朗南，分為兩個地塊，其中公營房屋集中在東邊的地塊中，此外也有不少私樓的土地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/myD7H8h_fyTAt1I.JTb_iA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/c629657ac5edfca256aa4b2191524fb0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmyD7H8h_fyTAt1I.JTb_iA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fc629657ac5edfca256aa4b2191524fb0&h=29a44cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新近的發展區是錦田南，位於石崗軍營與三號幹線巴士轉車站之間，中央是錦上路站上蓋項目，以及八鄉車廠項目，兩邊是公屋地盤，而巴士站附近更有一幅正由房委會研究當中的郊野公園邊緣土地，是附近的一個山窩，並不屬於郊野公園的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DR7W7t7HFNPrGTaIoDuDXQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTE0O2g9ODYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/3e44360d8afc32bff859278abb37a61d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDR7W7t7HFNPrGTaIoDuDXQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTE0O2g9ODYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F3e44360d8afc32bff859278abb37a61d&h=cce56ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了這三個發展區外，現時元朗還有兩個大型的公屋計劃，包括前朗邊中轉房屋地盤，現時已經拆卸，將會興建公屋，另外一幅位於丹桂村附近的地盤，也是以公屋發展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zD8rMHgMH4efk1RXmAqaUw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIwO2g9NzI1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/92c6ec01a5e66a313bd4e24e73890622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzD8rMHgMH4efk1RXmAqaUw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIwO2g9NzI1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F92c6ec01a5e66a313bd4e24e73890622&h=6aaeed26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了這三個發展區外，現時元朗還有兩個大型的公屋計劃，包括前朗邊中轉房屋地盤，現時已經拆卸，將會興建公屋，另外一幅位於丹桂村附近的地盤，也是以公屋發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E8%B6%A3%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%88%E8%84%AB%E8%8B%A6%E6%B5%B7%EF%BC%89-035843985.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B6%25A3%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25EF%25BC%2588%25E8%2584%25AB%25E8%258B%25A6%25E6%25B5%25B7%25EF%25BC%2589-035843985.html&d=73bTbcxjpI%2Fr7VMQknwB%2F8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=48a47572\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E8%B6%A3%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%88%E8%84%AB%E8%8B%A6%E6%B5%B7%EF%BC%89-035843985.html</a>"}]}